
'''''Platoon Leader''''' ni film ya Cannon Films yo mu 1988 yakozwe mu ntambara ya Vietnam kandi iyobowe na Aaron Norris ; ikinamo Michael Dudikoff na Michael DeLorenzo kandi yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. Rishingiye ku nyandiko ya James R. McDonough yibuka izina rimwe.

Iyi filime ivuga kubyerekeranye na liyetona mushya [[Viyetinamu|w’abasirikare bageze muri Vietnam]] kugira ngo yigarurire platoni ye ya mbere. Asanga agomba kwigaragaza no kugirirwa ikizere nabagabo banditswe niba ashaka kubayobora.

== Umugambi ==
Lt. Jeffrey Knight, umusirikare mushya wo mu Ishuri rya Gisirikare rya Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika, yajyanywe mu ndege ku birindiro biri muri Vietnam, aho ahurira na platon  ye, itsinda ry’abasirikare bakomeye b'intambara. Platon Serija McNamara asobanurira Knight ko platoni idakeneye umuyobozi ukurikiza amategeko. Ibikorwa bya Lt. Knight nabyo byamaganwa nabagabo be bose usibye Pvt. Parker, umukoresha wa radio.

Kuri rimwe mu irondo rye rya mbere, Knight yasitaye atitaye ku kirombe cyanjye cy'urugendo kandi aricwa. Parker noneho amaradiyo ya evac hanyuma McNamara ategeka ingabo kwimukira muri LZ kugirango zivemo . Nyuma, mu gihe Lt. Knight arimo gukira ibikomere mu bitaro bya Gisirikare, Major Flynn amubaza niba ashobora kongera gufata icyemezo maze Knight arabyemera. Knight asubizwa mu ndege asubira ku birindiro bya platon ariko ntiyakirwa n'abantu be asanga ibikoresho bye byabuze aho yari atuye, kuko batari biteze ko azagaruka. Bamenye ko Knight yagarutse, abasirikare bihutira gusubiza ibintu bye hanze y'ibiro bye mbere yuko agaruka. Knight amenya ko agomba gufata ubundi buryo kugirango abagabo be bamwubahe.

